title: Ipca Laboratories Ltd slips for fifth straight session
description: Ipca Laboratories Ltd is quoting at Rs 1382, down 0.95% on the day as on 13:19 IST on the NSE. The stock tumbled 40.2% in last one year as compared to a 8% rally in NIFTY and a 0.78% fall in the Nifty Pharma index.
